# Physical Map - Node Positions
# =============================
#
# Format: MAC_ADDRESS,X,Y,Z
#   - MAC_ADDRESS: Uppercase with colons (e.g., 1C:69:7A:AB:CD:EF)
#   - X, Y, Z: Position in meters relative to room origin
#
# The Z coordinate is typically the height above floor.
#
# Example room layout:
#
#     (0,4)─────────────────(4,4)
#       │                     │
#       │    Node2 (2,3)      │
#       │                     │
#       │  Node1      Node3   │
#       │  (1,1)      (3,1)   │
#       │                     │
#     (0,0)─────────────────(4,0)
#
# Uncomment and modify the lines below with your actual node MACs:
#
# 1C:69:7A:00:00:01,1.0,1.0,1.5
# 1C:69:7A:00:00:02,2.0,3.0,1.5
# 1C:69:7A:00:00:03,3.0,1.0,1.5
